{"tid":1681557,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎巴嫩和理非組170公里人鏈貫全國","createTime":"2019-10-29T13:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T16:44:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0fb87c05f9aa263c90f7282cd13cb62da56e6e","tid":1681557,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:35:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191028/5IKXAL5F6ZCZ26W3DVWRRMC7RA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191028%2F5IKXAL5F6ZCZ26W3DVWRRMC7RA%2F&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg6NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=53421c19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191028%2F5IKXAL5F6ZCZ26W3DVWRRMC7RA%2F&h=660637a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191028/5IKXAL5F6ZCZ26W3DVWRRMC7RA/</a><br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩和理非組170公里人鏈貫全國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/ps1b2jjDw-HNKGZWwJ7s2-gM1-E=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/2Z6MJVV7UZVWLCYNABZWR4ALGI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fps1b2jjDw-HNKGZWwJ7s2-gM1-E%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F2Z6MJVV7UZVWLCYNABZWR4ALGI.gif&h=979b91b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貝魯特民眾由南至北在全國築起人鏈。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩自月中上演反貪腐、反政府的示威，至今已持續11天，近17萬名示威者前日由南到北沿岸貫通國土，牽手組成170公里人鏈，展現WeConnect團結精神。黎巴嫩面積10,452平方米，約為香港10倍，人口就較少，有逾660萬。組人鏈的靈感來自連日示威中，組成人鏈阻隔警民衝突的黎巴嫩婦女；不相識的參與者午後開始集結，沿阿卡爾牽手到西頓，穿越貝魯特、的黎波里等海岸城市，到當地時間下午4時左右便成形。很多人以國旗包裹身子，唱着國歌。由於人鏈是沿海岸公路旁組成，故交通暢順，未有造成阻塞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自發補缺口<br />\n<br />\n僅以兩天時間籌辦活動的哈穆德博士（Sally Hammoud）說，活動象徵意義在於表明示威立場，並非要擾亂國家，也不要刺激或妨礙他人行動自由：「這是為了向世界展示我們團結一致，不會被分裂，最重要是我們很和平。」<br />\n<br />\n哈穆德說，參與者靠手機互傳資訊，在沒有大台、對講機指揮或交通接載下，民眾自發坐巴士到「缺人」的地點連接空缺，有車的亦義載其他示威者到場，人鏈就自然而然組成。其間亦非全無阻滯，哈穆德說反對派曾威嚇參與者，要長期牽手維持人鏈亦不容易，但活動總算完成，對革命是一支強心針，有助推動美好的改變。<br />\n<br />\n另一主辦者兼女演員赫瓦姆（Yara Khawam）說，人鏈是象徵愛的行動，「我們得悉政府如何分隔各宗派，逼我們憎恨對方，我們才明白到大家如何渴望牽手及在一起」。<br />\n<br />\n美國有新聞網絡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/ySTtmXkEkAftnMGue8trbdcb24E=/802x599/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/IHJ5UFCO7QJ3L45M2PH5T6LNIQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FySTtmXkEkAftnMGue8trbdcb24E%3D%2F802x599%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FIHJ5UFCO7QJ3L45M2PH5T6LNIQ.gif&h=35b6e585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者高舉黎巴嫩國旗。美聯社<br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"bc354e4fbeac1dc27eb0be2f655a1097f01d3b04","tid":1681557,"uid":47605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:35:46.000Z","msg":"我們早前在Telegram成立了手足匿名搵工平台，助手足自行尋找明白其情況的本地良心僱主，幫助他們在漫長保釋（可能講緊一、兩年時間的排期）或長期夢境中，有工開有野做有糧出，同時又可以滿足保釋條件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680524</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/findagoodboss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffindagoodboss&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg6NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=20a08c21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/findagoodboss</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a1c5dc4e69105b7f962693a198581b6605d094","tid":1681557,"uid":25858,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"香港又輸出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7dfdaf17f3f29d64c8785380d2e0181be5ff8b2","tid":1681557,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:37:47.000Z","msg":"輸出革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1f8e353e8bff68a7ac5e22272c29247c5a042f","tid":1681557,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"